---
title: Cheesy American Plant-Based Mince Chilli Nachos with Corn Chips & Tomato-Corn Salsa
description: We’re doing nachos like no other because they’re veggie-fied with a saucy and spiced plant-based mince that will have your
mouth watering. You can go all out with the toppings too, with a creamy mayo and tomato-corn salsa to tie it all together!

